<eesti>Sisses&otilde;idukeelu kehtivusaja muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of period of validity of prohibition on entry </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Siseminister, kuulanud &auml;ra tema poolt moodustatud n&otilde;uandva komisjoni seisukoha, t&uuml;histab v&otilde;i l&uuml;hendab sisses&otilde;idukeelu kehtivusaega v&auml;lismaalase taotlusel v&otilde;i valitsusasutuse algatusel, kui sisses&otilde;idukeelu kohaldamise alus on muutunud v&otilde;i &auml;ra langenud. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) The Minister of Internal Affairs, after considering the position of the advisory committee formed by him or her, shall annul the prohibition on entry or shorten the period of validity of the prohibition on entry at the request of the alien or on the initiative of a government agency if the basis for application of the prohibition on entry has changed or ceased to exist. </inglise>
<eesti>(26.10.99 j&otilde;ust.25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </eesti>
<inglise>(26.10.99 entered into force 25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Siseminister, kuulanud &auml;ra tema poolt moodustatud n&otilde;uandva komisjoni seisukoha, v&otilde;ib v&auml;lismaalase taotlusel v&otilde;i valitsusasutuse algatusel sisses&otilde;idukeelu t&uuml;histada v&otilde;i l&uuml;hendada selle kehtivusaega: </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Minister of Internal Affairs, after considering the position of the advisory committee formed by him or her, may annul the prohibition on entry or shorten the period of validity of the prohibition on entry at the request of the alien or on the initiative of a government agency: </inglise>
<eesti>(26.10.99 j&otilde;ust.25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </eesti>
<inglise>(26.10.99 entered into force 25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </inglise>
<eesti>1) kui k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 31 l&otilde;ikes 3 loetletud asjaolud on muutunud; </eesti>
<inglise>1) if the circumstances listed in subsection 31 (1) of this Act have changed; </inglise>
<eesti>2) humaansetel kaalutlustel, kui sellega ei ohustata riigi julgeolekut ega avalikku korda. </eesti>
<inglise>2) on humane considerations if national security and public order are not endangered thereby. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Siseminister, kuulanud &auml;ra tema poolt moodustatud n&otilde;uandva komisjoni seisukoha, v&otilde;ib valitsusasutuse algatusel pikendada sisses&otilde;idukeelu kehtivusaega v&otilde;i asendada t&auml;htajalise sisses&otilde;idukeelu alalisega, kui v&auml;lismaalase suhtes ilmnevad t&auml;iendavad k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 29 l&otilde;ikes 1 s&auml;testatud sisses&otilde;idukeelu kohaldamise alused. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) The Minister of Internal Affairs, after considering the position of the advisory committee formed by him or her, may extend the period of validity of the prohibition on entry, or replace a temporary prohibition on entry with a permanent prohibition on entry, on the initiative of a government agency and if additional bases for the application of a prohibition on entry provided for in subsection 29 (1) of this Act become evident with regard to the alien. </inglise>
<eesti>T&auml;htaja pikendamise v&otilde;i t&auml;htajalise sisses&otilde;idukeelu alalisega asendamise suhtes kohaldatakse k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect; 31 l&otilde;igetes 3-5 s&auml;testatut. </eesti>
<inglise>The provisions of subsections 31 (3) -(5) of this Act apply with regard to extension of the period of validity or with regard to replacement of a temporary prohibition on entry with a permanent prohibition on entry. </inglise>
<eesti>(26.10.99 j&otilde;ust.25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </eesti>
<inglise>(26.10.99 entered into force 25.11.99 - RT I 1999, 84, 762) </inglise>
