<eesti>Sisses&otilde;idukeelu kohaldamine v&auml;lismaalasele, kelle sisses&otilde;it Eestisse on enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist t&otilde;kestatud </eesti>
<inglise>Application of prohibition on entry to alien whose entry into Estonia was prevented prior to entry into force of this Act </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;lismaalase suhtes, kelle sisses&otilde;it Eestisse on enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist t&otilde;kestatud, kohaldatakse sisses&otilde;idukeeldu vastavalt k&auml;esoleva seaduse 5. peat&uuml;kile. </eesti>
<inglise>A prohibition on entry with regard to an alien whose entry into Estonia was prevented prior to the entry into force of this Act applies in accordance with Chapter 5 of this Act. </inglise>
