<eesti>V&auml;ljasaadetavate kinnipidamise otsuste t&auml;ideviimine kuni v&auml;ljasaatmislaagri ehitamiseni </eesti>
<inglise>Application of decisions concerning detention of persons to be expelled until construction of expulsion centre </inglise>
<eesti>Kuni v&auml;ljasaatmislaagri ehitamiseni ja vastuv&otilde;tmiseni viiakse v&auml;ljasaadetavate kinnipidamise otsused t&auml;ide kinnise vangla teistest osakondadest eraldatud osakonnas. </eesti>
<inglise>Until an expulsion centre is constructed and accepted, the judgments concerning the detention of persons to be expelled shall be enforced in isolated wards of maximum-security prisons. </inglise>
<eesti>V&auml;ljasaadetavat v&otilde;ib kinni pidada ka politsei arestimajas, kuid mitte &uuml;le k&uuml;mne p&auml;eva j&auml;rjest. </eesti>
<inglise>Persons to be expelled may also be detained in police houses of detention, however not for longer than for ten consecutive days. </inglise>
