<eesti>5) muu seadusest tulenev v&otilde;i seaduse alusel haldusaktiga antud luba v&auml;lismaalase Eestis viibimiseks." </eesti>
<inglise>5) other permission arising from law, or permission granted by administrative legislation on the basis of law for the alien to stay in Estonia." </inglise>
